  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chop the Tree</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.poster.avif?t=1773766284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.webm?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.mp4?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack away at a massive tree that showers the ground with logs, gold, and power-ups.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Permanent Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.poster.avif?t=1773766284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.webm?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.mp4?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned logs on a massive skill tree packed with automation, special logs, potions, and wild synergies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize Your Playstyle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d8432ffb94016ad6bb38d867a8d30627.poster.avif?t=1773766284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d8432ffb94016ad6bb38d867a8d30627.webm?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d8432ffb94016ad6bb38d867a8d30627.mp4?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock axes and characters to maximize your chopping potential.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Special Logs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/461d60896746259e3dfef4a03d54d7e3.avif?t=1773766284\" width=601 height=339 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger lightning strikes, freeze time, or magnetize the entire screen.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chop the Tree</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.poster.avif?t=1773766284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.webm?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d1de571fb3d43d7853e0b5d48c53b7bb.mp4?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack away at a massive tree that showers the ground with logs, gold, and power-ups.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Permanent Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.poster.avif?t=1773766284\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.webm?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/b639dc18106d43a629d09e40660a796c.mp4?t=1773766284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your hard-earned logs on a massive skill tree packed with automation, special logs, potions, and wild synergies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize Your Playstyle</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4298880/extras/d8432ffb94016ad6bb38d867a