      "review_text": "能爽，但只有前期有新鲜感，中期升级不够平滑，点一个升级就需要挂两三把，后期机制都解锁了就只剩数值提升，内容不多，寿命大约5小时，首发17.6不算很值。\n[hr][/hr]\nIt's enjoyable at first, with some nice freshness in the early game. The mid-game upgrades feel a bit uneven though — unlocking just one often requires playing through a couple of runs. Once all the mechanics are unlocked later on, it mostly comes down to numerical improvements with little else new. Overall there's not a huge amount of content, and the game lasts around 5 hours. At the ￥17.60 launch price, it feels like only okay value.",
